In [5]:
import seaborn as sns
sns.set(style="white")
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.figure(figsize=(6,8))
fontsize=20

cmap = sns.cubehelix_palette(start=3, light=1, as_cmap=True)

hb = plt.hexbin(J_Ks_b309,Ks_b309, gridsize=90, bins="log",cmap=cmap)

plt.plot(J_Ks_microb309,Ks_microb309,'^k',ms=15)
plt.title('Tile b309', fontsize=20)

plt.yticks(fontsize=15)
plt.xticks(fontsize=15)

cb = plt.colorbar(hb)
cb.set_label(r'$\rm Log(Nstars)$',fontsize=fontsize)
cb.ax.tick_params(labelsize=15)

plt.xlabel(r'$ \rm J-K_{s} $',fontsize=fontsize)
plt.ylabel(r"$\rm K_{s}$ [mag]",fontsize=fontsize)

plt.xlim(-0.2,3)
plt.ylim(11.5,17.3)
plt.gca().invert_yaxis()
plt.savefig('CMD_b309.eps',dpi=100)

#sns.cubehelix_palette(start=0, light=1, as_cmap=True)

hb = plt.hexbin(c3,m4, gridsize=gridsize,bins="log",cmap=cmap)
plt.yticks(fontsize=15)
plt.xticks(fontsize=15)

#plt.plot(J_Ks_microb296,Ks_microb296,'^k',ms=10)
plt.errorbar(c3_micros, m4_micros, xerr=ec3_micros, yerr=em4_micros,fmt='ok',ms=ms)

plt.title('Tile b296', fontsize=20)

c = 0
for i,j in zip(c3_micros, m4_micros):
    plt.annotate('%s' %ID[c], xy=(i,j), xytext=(-18,10), textcoords='offset points',fontsize=13)
    c +=1

cb = plt.colorbar(hb)
cb.set_label(r'${\rm Log(Nstars)}$',fontsize=fontsize)
cb.ax.tick_params(labelsize=15)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.figure(figsize=(6,8))
fontsize=20

cmap = plt.get_cmap('Blues')

#sns.cubehelix_palette(start=0, light=1, as_cmap=True)

hb = plt.hexbin(J_Ks_b309,Ks_b309, gridsize=gridsize,bins="log",cmap=cmap)
plt.yticks(fontsize=15)
plt.xticks(fontsize=15)

plt.plot(J_Ks_microb309,Ks_microb309,'ko',ms=ms)
#plt.errorbar(J_Ks_microb309,Ks_microb309, xerr=errJ_Ks/2., yerr=err_Ks,fmt='ok',ms=ms)
plt.title('Tile b309', fontsize=20)

c = 0
for i,j in zip(J_Ks_microb309,Ks_microb309):   
    
    if ID[c] == 'm0040':
        plt.annotate('%s' %ID[c], xy=(i,j), xytext=(-14,28), textcoords='offset points',fontsize=13)
    else:
        plt.annotate('%s' %ID[c], xy=(i,j), xytext=(-14,15), textcoords='offset points',fontsize=13)    
    c +=1  
        
cb = plt.colorbar(hb)
cb.set_label(r'${\rm Log(Nstars)}$',fontsize=fontsize)
cb.ax.tick_params(labelsize=15)

plt.xlabel(r'${\rm (J-K_{s})_{0}}$',fontsize=fontsize)
plt.ylabel(r"${\rm K_{s,0}}$ [mag]",fontsize=fontsize)

plt.xlim(-1,2)
plt.ylim(11.,17)

plt.gca().invert_yaxis()
plt.savefig('CMD_b309.jpg',dpi=500,format='jpg')
